      "content": "hey i'm looking at moving my emergency fund into a savings account. i have about $5000 right now sitting in my checking. i found three different high yield options: 4.1% APY, 4.35% APY, and 4.5% APY. can you tell me how much interest i'd make on each one after a year if i dont touch it?",
